      "content": "Wait, really? You're saying originalism is \"undeniably\" more stable? I thought you were supposed to be a neutral scholar. If the living constitution theory is just \"judicial activism,\" then doesn't that mean the whole idea of evolving standards of decency is basically just a legal lie?",
